comments[3]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-07-10T05:53:25.929Z",codex-root-20260709,"Verification evidence 2026-07-10: full sandbox suite passed 270 files / 5,505 tests with exact 100% statements, branches, functions, and lines. pm test-all over the seven active items passed 8 linked commands with 0 failures and 1 duplicate-safe skip. pnpm typecheck, contracts:check, lint (ESLint + 0 jscpd clones + static quality/token budget), docs-skills, context-eval, security scan, and audit all passed. Live CodeFactor reports A+ and 0 issues. Fresh packed npm install at /tmp/pm-cli-sdk-path-proof-XIsSsh activated 11 bundled packages in a path-target tracker, left caller extension files at zero, and passed CLI/SDK context plus isolated doctor with zero blocking failures. pm health is clean and history drift is zero."
  "2026-07-10T06:23:44.841Z",codex-root-20260709,"Greptile pre-push review 388e369e found and we fixed two result-contract edges: wildcard multi-package details now set installed_all from the aggregate success bit, and SDK recovery next_steps clone help commands rather than aliasing the help_commands array. Focused 149 tests, full 5,505-test exact 100/100/100/100 coverage, typecheck, contracts, lint, static quality, and zero-clone gates pass after the fixes."
  "2026-07-10T07:08:15.574Z",codex-root-20260709,"PR #491 review follow-up: Greptile T-Rex reproduced diagnostic loss when one target in a multi-package install returned ok=false. Added a failing-first unit contract plus real CLI integration with one valid and one broken package; failed rows now preserve runtime_activation_status, activation_diagnostics, command_discovery, and verification. CodeRabbit public wording was updated to package testing. Full coverage and strict quality gates pass."
